<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="assets/stylesheets/my_style.css">
</head>

<!-- Carousel ================================================== -->
    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide round-carousel" data-ride="carousel">
      <!-- Indicators -->
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
        <div class="item active">
          <img class="first-slide custom-pic" src="assets/pasta.jpg" alt="First slide">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
              <h1 class="banner-title">Recipes</h1>
              <h3>No need to frantically google "romantic dinners" anymore!</h3>
              <%= link_to "View Recipes", recipes_url, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <img class="second-slide custom-pic" src="assets/salad.jpg" alt="Second slide">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
              <h1 class="banner-title">Drinks</h1>
              <p>Let's get faded (not to be confused with "Fading", which is what always happens to me when I drink.</p>
              <%= link_to "View Drinks", drinks_url, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <img class="third-slide custom-pic" src="assets/counter.jpg" alt="Third slide">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
              <h1 class="banner-title">Categories</h1>
              <h1>Feeling organized?</h1>
              <p>Browse recipes by category.</p>
              <%= link_to "View Categories", categories_url, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div><!-- /.carousel -->


      <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Try new recipes<span class="text-muted"> Chicken Pozole</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Cooking is a fantastic test of compatibility. It involves planning (WHAT ARE WE GOING TO EAT TOMORROW?), attention-to-detail (There's a difference between salted and unsalted butter), and patience. Once you and yours are able to suffer together through the throgs of the grocery store lines on Super Bowl Sunday, you know you can make it through anytihng. And you'll be rewarded with some delicious chicken pozole! (= </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block custom-pic" src="assets/pozole.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Oh yeah, he's that good. <span class="text-muted">See for yourself.</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Checkout all of these awesome recipes Chris and I have made: homemade tortillini. Chicken Tinga Tacos. Drunk Mac and Cheese. Seared Scallops and Risotto. Frozen Pizza. You won't be disappointed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7">
          <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block custom-pic" src="assets/chris_cooks.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">And lastly, drinks. <span class="text-muted">Checkmate.</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">We all know that no good meal is complete without drinks. When you want to class it up with a cocktail, you can never go wrong (or just drink wine).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block custom-pic" src="assets/drinks.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->


      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <footer>
        <p class="pull-right"><a href="#">Back to top</a></p>
        <p>&copy; 2017 Rokey</p>
      </footer>

    </div><!-- /.container -->